<body>
   <div class="contain">
    <div class="top-section">
    <h1> How to became a Professional Gamer after completing your class 10th</h1>
    <p>
        Select a game that you are passionate about and want to compete in professionally. It can be any game, ranging from popular esports titles like League of Legends, Dota 2, and Counter-Strike: Global Offensive to lesser-known games.

    </p>
    </div> 
     <div class="timeline">
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Develop your skills</h2>
                <p>
                    Dedicate time and effort to developing your gaming skills. Watch tutorials, participate in online communities, and practice regularly to improve your gameplay.

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
              <h2> Join a team
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Join a professional gaming team or create your own team. Teams offer support, training, and the opportunity to compete in tournaments.
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Participate in tournaments</h2>
                <p>
                    Participate in online and offline tournaments to gain experience and exposure. This will help you build your reputation and increase your chances of being noticed by potential sponsors.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Build your brand
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Create a personal brand and promote it on social media platforms like Twitch, YouTube, and Twitter. Interact with your followers and create engaging content to build your fanbase.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>
                    Secure sponsorships
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Once you have a substantial following, you can approach potential sponsors for brand deals, merchandise sales, and other collaborations.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div><div class="section">
            <div class="bead"></div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>An overall journey
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Becoming a professional gamer requires dedication, hard work, and the ability to learn and adapt to changing trends. It is a highly competitive field, and success depends on a combination of skill, strategy, and luck.


                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
      
     </div>
   </div>
